            <title>[HADOOP-8781] hadoop-config.sh should add JAVA_LIBRARY_PATH to LD_LIBRARY_PATH</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-8781</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
